    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Euochin furvus comb. nov., holotype male. A Right palp, prolateral view (horizontal flip); B Same, ventral view; C Same, retrolateral view; D Left chelicera; E Habitus, dorsal view and original label. Abbreviations: E embolus; ED embolic disc; FB fusion bubble; RSDL retrolateral sperm duct loop; RTA retrolateral tibial apophysis; SD sperm duct; T tegulum; TL tegular lobe." ;
